text: Zbigniew Klimowski (born 18 January 1967) is a Polish ski jumper. He competed in the large hill event at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Poland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:People from Nowy Targ
